RACE.FOOTNOTES: SOUNDS SPOOKY coaxed from the gate, chased four then three wide under coaxing from the three-eighths, angled six wide into upper stretch, rallied to take narrow command a furlong out, dug in dueling to the finish and gamely held on to prevail. STEADY PROGRESS three wide in pursuit, came under coaxing half a mile from home, went seven wide into upper stretch, offered up a bid to latch on the top pair a furlong out, then got repelled while keeping on to secure the show honors. THAT'S MY BUSINESS coaxed from the start, dueled from the two path, tucked inside through the turn coming under coaxing at the three-eighths, spun three wide for home and weakened in the late stages. DISTURBED chased along the inside under coaxing from the half mile pole, spun just off the inside into upper stretch and tired. AWESOME WEAPON chased four to five wide under coaxing from the seven-sixteenths, spun four wide for home, trailed.

VALLARAND was urged along at the rear, saved ground on the turn, came five wide into upper stretch and was no factor then reported to have bled while walked off.
